1
00:01:09,960 --> 00:01:11,090
This letter reports

2
00:01:11,320 --> 00:01:14,039
that relevant city leaders are involved in the case.

3
00:01:14,039 --> 00:01:16,920
If the contents of this letter are true,

4
00:01:18,080 --> 00:01:20,340
this case will be even more complicated.

5
00:01:20,640 --> 00:01:22,500
Whether it's an internal problem

6
00:01:22,760 --> 00:01:24,520
or interference from external forces,

7
00:01:24,520 --> 00:01:26,120
we need to find out the truth.

8
00:01:26,400 --> 00:01:27,400
No matter who it is,

9
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,680
we must root them out.

10
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:32,250
We also need conclusive evidence.

11
00:01:34,160 --> 00:01:34,620
Indeed.

12
00:01:35,200 --> 00:01:38,039
After all, many things can't be investigated openly.

13
00:01:38,039 --> 00:01:40,170
This evidence alone is hardly enough.

14
00:01:41,520 --> 00:01:42,250
Then, Chief,

15
00:01:42,720 --> 00:01:43,240
we...

16
00:01:44,000 --> 00:01:45,800
Just do your part.

17
00:01:46,479 --> 00:01:47,810
If anything goes wrong,

18
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:50,450
the Commissar and I will cover for you.

19
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,120
Thank you for your trust, Chief.

20
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:54,120
Old Wu, I'll go to the Provincial Department

21
00:01:54,120 --> 00:01:56,920
to clear some obstacles for their investigation.

22
00:01:57,800 --> 00:01:58,200
Chief.

23
00:01:58,560 --> 00:02:00,640
Then we'll investigate with confidence.

24
00:02:00,640 --> 00:02:01,080
Okay.

25
00:02:04,720 --> 00:02:05,480
Captain Shen.

26
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,600
Thank you, Xiao Wang.

27
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:07,060
Xiao Li.

28
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:09,000
Let Team Two handle the legal education task.

29
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,039
We have a new mission.

30
00:02:10,039 --> 00:02:11,240
Got it, Captain Shen.

31
00:02:18,720 --> 00:02:19,720
What do you think?

32
00:02:20,400 --> 00:02:21,600
Just speak your mind.

33
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,820
The chief wants us to merge the cases.

34
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:25,960
Then next, we need to figure out

35
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,160
who sent this letter,

36
00:02:27,520 --> 00:02:28,880
and what role Ye Qiming

37
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,160
played in this case,

38
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:31,800
and why he died suddenly.

39
00:02:32,200 --> 00:02:34,600
The timing of this letter is quite intriguing.

40
00:02:34,600 --> 00:02:36,600
It appeared right after Ye Qiming died.

41
00:02:36,600 --> 00:02:37,200
Which means Ye Qiming

42
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:38,800
most likely knew the sender.

43
00:02:39,240 --> 00:02:40,160
We're going to investigate him anyway.

44
00:02:40,160 --> 00:02:41,760
Let's look into it together.

45
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,280
Will that tip them off?

46
00:02:43,760 --> 00:02:46,480
On the surface, we are investigating Ye Qiming's case.

47
00:02:46,480 --> 00:02:48,760
But in reality, only we know what we're looking for.

48
00:02:48,760 --> 00:02:49,760
Why didn't I notice before

49
00:02:49,760 --> 00:02:51,160
that you had this side to you?

50
00:02:51,160 --> 00:02:51,760
What side?

51
00:02:52,480 --> 00:02:53,840
The meticulous side.

52
00:02:55,640 --> 00:02:56,770
We're familiar now.

53
00:02:58,079 --> 00:02:59,280
Alright, let's work.

54
00:03:07,000 --> 00:03:07,720
Okay, Captain Zhang.

55
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:08,320
Let me head back first.

56
00:03:08,320 --> 00:03:09,180
Okay, alright.

57
00:03:11,120 --> 00:03:11,720
Take care.

58
00:03:11,720 --> 00:03:12,720
Thanks for your hard work.

59
00:03:12,720 --> 00:03:13,180
Mr. Jin,

60
00:03:13,520 --> 00:03:14,400
can you help us with this?

61
00:03:14,400 --> 00:03:14,800
Got it.

62
00:03:14,960 --> 00:03:15,920
I'll do it as soon as possible.

63
00:03:15,920 --> 00:03:16,320
Thank you, Mr. Jin.

64
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:16,920
Thank you.

65
00:03:17,680 --> 00:03:18,210
Zhao, Li.

66
00:03:18,320 --> 00:03:18,760
Captain Shen.

67
00:03:18,760 --> 00:03:20,020
Master, Captain Shen,

68
00:03:20,040 --> 00:03:21,680
this is Captain Zhang from the neighboring city.

69
00:03:21,680 --> 00:03:22,280
Hello.

70
00:03:22,280 --> 00:03:22,720
Hello.

71
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,920
It's very similar to the description you gave.

72
00:03:24,920 --> 00:03:25,880
When was it found?

73
00:03:25,880 --> 00:03:26,720
At 8:00 this morning,

74
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:27,920
an old man was fishing by the river

75
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:29,040
and found a woven bag.

76
00:03:29,040 --> 00:03:30,160
He thought it was garbage,

77
00:03:30,160 --> 00:03:31,560
but when he opened it, it was body parts.

78
00:03:31,560 --> 00:03:32,520
He was frightened.

79
00:03:32,520 --> 00:03:33,520
It floated quite far.

80
00:03:33,520 --> 00:03:34,520
It seems the killer

81
00:03:34,520 --> 00:03:36,920
threw the body into the river from the cliff.

82
00:03:36,920 --> 00:03:38,920
Because it was raining heavily and the current was fast that day,

83
00:03:38,920 --> 00:03:40,160
it floated downstream.

84
00:03:40,160 --> 00:03:41,640
Fortunately, you asked Xiao Li

85
00:03:41,640 --> 00:03:42,360
to give me a heads-up beforehand.

86
00:03:42,360 --> 00:03:43,800
We didn't touch anything.

87
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,760
It was just a wild guess.

88
00:03:44,760 --> 00:03:45,360
Thank you.

89
00:03:45,520 --> 00:03:48,050
You're welcome. Hope you crack the case soon.

90
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:50,329
Definitely.

91
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,760
Xia Lin inherited

92
00:03:52,760 --> 00:03:54,220
30% of Ye Qiming's shares.

93
00:03:54,520 --> 00:03:57,240
She holds the most shares on the board of directors now.

94
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:59,770
Then make her voluntarily give up her shares.

95
00:03:59,960 --> 00:04:00,890
It's time to act.

96
00:04:05,080 --> 00:04:05,600
Ye Yuan.

97
00:04:08,480 --> 00:04:08,840
Mr. Xia.

98
00:04:08,840 --> 00:04:09,440
Officer Jiang.

99
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,000
Officer Shen.

100
00:04:10,000 --> 00:04:10,520
Mr. Xia,

101
00:04:11,360 --> 00:04:12,420
please take a seat.

102
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:15,800
Mr. Xia.

103
00:04:16,279 --> 00:04:17,120
Is there any clue

104
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:18,320
you forgot to tell us?

105
00:04:20,320 --> 00:04:21,040
As you know,

106
00:04:21,320 --> 00:04:22,200
Tongda

107
00:04:22,360 --> 00:04:25,120
is currently in the process of being acquired by Xincheng.

108
00:04:25,120 --> 00:04:26,440
So if there is any reason

109
00:04:26,440 --> 00:04:28,100
for Ye Qiming to kill someone,

110
00:04:28,280 --> 00:04:30,610
I think it would be because of the company.

111
00:04:30,800 --> 00:04:32,120
If I remember correctly,

112
00:04:32,120 --> 00:04:34,380
Tongda rose to prominence five years ago

113
00:04:34,440 --> 00:04:36,200
thanks to a project in the eastern suburbs,

114
00:04:36,200 --> 00:04:36,640
right?

115
00:04:37,640 --> 00:04:38,159
Yes.

116
00:04:39,120 --> 00:04:41,980
That was also the point when our family broke apart.

117
00:04:43,400 --> 00:04:44,460
Why do you say that?

118
00:04:45,880 --> 00:04:47,720
Because that was when Yu Na

119
00:04:47,840 --> 00:04:49,900
brought this project to the company.

120
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:50,800
Linlin,

121
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:51,620
Linlin,

122
00:04:52,680 --> 00:04:53,600
you're back!

123
00:04:54,159 --> 00:04:55,159
I missed you so much.

124
00:04:55,159 --> 00:04:55,880
Are you tired?

125
00:04:55,880 --> 00:04:56,540
Not too bad.

126
00:04:56,840 --> 00:04:57,960
Let me get you some water.

127
00:04:57,960 --> 00:04:58,600
Thanks.

128
00:04:59,040 --> 00:05:00,300
I found a talent today.

129
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,000
Her name is Yu Na.

130
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,440
Yu Na?

131
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:05,240
Is she pretty?

132
00:05:05,840 --> 00:05:06,500
She's okay.

133
00:05:07,600 --> 00:05:08,800
She's smart like you.

134
00:05:09,040 --> 00:05:10,400
She learns everything very fast

135
00:05:10,400 --> 00:05:11,730
and catches on quickly.

136
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:13,160
Is she smarter,

137
00:05:13,400 --> 00:05:14,200
or am I?

138
00:05:14,800 --> 00:05:16,080
Of course you are.

139
00:05:16,760 --> 00:05:18,160
I told you a long time ago,

140
00:05:18,480 --> 00:05:19,720
if you came to help at the company,

141
00:05:19,720 --> 00:05:21,760
our company would have gone public by now.

142
00:05:21,760 --> 00:05:23,400
Then maybe I should think about it.

143
00:05:23,400 --> 00:05:25,460
Now, the board of directors of Tongda

144
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:27,400
is single-handedly controlled by Yu Na.

145
00:05:27,400 --> 00:05:28,130
So I'm afraid

146
00:05:28,320 --> 00:05:29,840
she might frame Ye Yuan

147
00:05:30,000 --> 00:05:31,480
in order to take away my shares.

148
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,600
That's why I came today

149
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:34,000
to ask for your help.

150
00:05:35,880 --> 00:05:37,280
The East Suburb project.

151
00:05:42,000 --> 00:05:42,600
Song Qing.

152
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,640
Song Qing.

153
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,060
Somebody help!

154
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:49,360
Somebody help!

155
00:05:50,480 --> 00:05:52,280
The ambulance will be here soon.

156
00:05:52,680 --> 00:05:53,240
Sister.

157
00:05:57,280 --> 00:05:58,480
Give it to Shen Feng.

158
00:06:01,880 --> 00:06:02,480
Song Qing.

159
00:06:03,480 --> 00:06:04,240
Song Qing.

160
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,320
Thank you for the clues you provided today.

161
00:06:07,320 --> 00:06:08,520
That's all for today.

162
00:06:08,760 --> 00:06:09,400
We...

163
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:10,840
Good work.

164
00:06:12,280 --> 00:06:13,080
Officer Shen.

165
00:06:13,320 --> 00:06:14,780
I want to talk to you alone.

166
00:06:17,040 --> 00:06:17,500
Xiao Li.

167
00:06:20,840 --> 00:06:22,970
Song Qing's death wasn't an accident.

168
00:06:33,159 --> 00:06:33,760
Shen Feng.

169
00:06:36,400 --> 00:06:37,600
You're acting weird.

170
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:38,800
What's wrong?

171
00:06:39,960 --> 00:06:42,090
Song Qing's death wasn't an accident.

172
00:06:42,159 --> 00:06:42,680
What?

173
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:45,980
Leave me alone.

174
00:06:56,240 --> 00:06:56,840
Shen Feng.

175
00:06:57,480 --> 00:06:58,640
I think... I...

176
00:07:08,840 --> 00:07:09,370
Chief Wu.

177
00:07:13,280 --> 00:07:14,340
Where is Shen Feng?

178
00:07:15,440 --> 00:07:16,240
He's outside.

179
00:07:16,520 --> 00:07:18,580
I was just about to go looking for you.

180
00:07:21,960 --> 00:07:22,400
What?

181
00:07:23,120 --> 00:07:24,520
Any progress on the case?

182
00:07:24,680 --> 00:07:25,680
We have some clues

183
00:07:26,000 --> 00:07:28,130
regarding the whistleblower letter.

184
00:07:28,840 --> 00:07:30,100
Seek truth from facts.

185
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,360
Investigate

186
00:07:31,760 --> 00:07:32,560
as you see fit.

187
00:07:33,200 --> 00:07:34,440
Don't have any concerns.

188
00:07:34,440 --> 00:07:35,720
The provincial department said

189
00:07:35,720 --> 00:07:37,250
to investigate it to the end

190
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:38,520
so evil forces

191
00:07:39,440 --> 00:07:40,640
have nowhere to hide.

192
00:07:41,080 --> 00:07:41,540
You guys

193
00:07:42,560 --> 00:07:43,420
go do it boldly.

194
00:07:44,120 --> 00:07:45,120
We got your back.

195
00:07:46,880 --> 00:07:47,880
Thanks, Chief Wu.

196
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,250
There's one more thing.

197
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,200
I...

198
00:07:52,240 --> 00:07:53,500
What do you want to say?

199
00:07:56,840 --> 00:07:58,700
I want to reopen Song Qing's case.

200
00:07:59,800 --> 00:08:00,600
For Shen Feng?

201
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,160
No,

202
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:02,920
for Song Qing.

203
00:08:05,280 --> 00:08:06,210
Hasn't this case

204
00:08:06,720 --> 00:08:07,960
already been closed?

205
00:08:08,760 --> 00:08:10,800
They said it was an accident.

206
00:08:12,600 --> 00:08:14,860
I'm afraid it's not as simple as we think.

207
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,520
Is it related

208
00:08:17,960 --> 00:08:18,840
to this case?

209
00:08:19,440 --> 00:08:21,100
It's related to Tongda Group.

210
00:08:22,000 --> 00:08:23,080
Tongda Group?

211
00:08:28,400 --> 00:08:30,060
Since it's handed over to you,

212
00:08:30,280 --> 00:08:31,810
how you want to investigate

213
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:33,280
is up to you.

214
00:08:33,840 --> 00:08:34,570
I don't care.

215
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,320
But one thing,

216
00:08:37,440 --> 00:08:38,500
do it beautifully.

217
00:08:39,400 --> 00:08:40,330
At the same time,

218
00:08:41,440 --> 00:08:42,840
pay attention to safety.

219
00:08:43,799 --> 00:08:44,240
Yes.

220
00:08:50,520 --> 00:08:51,850
What's wrong, Chief Wu?

221
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:54,760
This case back then,

222
00:08:55,440 --> 00:08:57,300
Shen Feng handled it personally.

223
00:08:58,880 --> 00:09:00,140
It hit him pretty hard.

224
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:03,240
You need to keep things under control.

225
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,040
I understand.

226
00:09:04,040 --> 00:09:04,970
I'll be careful.

227
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,850
Take care, Chief Wu.

228
00:09:39,920 --> 00:09:42,180
You're quite observant, Captain Jiang.

229
00:09:43,480 --> 00:09:44,720
You're overthinking it.

230
00:09:44,720 --> 00:09:46,520
I just came to get some fresh air.

231
00:09:52,240 --> 00:09:54,170
I've looked into Song Qing's case.

232
00:09:55,000 --> 00:09:56,860
I've been running away from this.

233
00:09:59,040 --> 00:10:00,300
Because I feel guilty.

234
00:10:02,960 --> 00:10:03,880
But I just wanted to

235
00:10:03,880 --> 00:10:05,680
try my best to find out the truth.

236
00:10:08,360 --> 00:10:09,820
Then keep investigating.

237
00:10:12,600 --> 00:10:15,400
Sometimes hard work doesn't lead to good results.

238
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:18,640
Actually, in every case,

239
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:21,340
there's an invisible pair of eyes

240
00:10:21,600 --> 00:10:23,200
watching us from somewhere.

241
00:10:25,080 --> 00:10:27,280
But as long as they let their guard down,

242
00:10:27,280 --> 00:10:28,540
even just for a moment,

243
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:32,360
we earn the right to look them in the eye.

244
00:10:33,200 --> 00:10:34,000
Then the truth

245
00:10:35,040 --> 00:10:36,770
will definitely come to light.

246
00:10:39,440 --> 00:10:40,040
Shen Feng.

247
00:10:42,720 --> 00:10:44,520
I've reopened Song Qing's case.

248
00:10:45,360 --> 00:10:46,620
Next, I want to ask you,

249
00:10:47,840 --> 00:10:49,040
do you want to join us?

250
00:11:07,680 --> 00:11:09,120
Since she committed a crime,

251
00:11:09,120 --> 00:11:10,520
we can't let her get away.

252
00:11:11,360 --> 00:11:13,520
We are going to Yu Na's house to arrest her now.

253
00:11:13,520 --> 00:11:15,320
Leave the villa to the four of us.

254
00:11:15,400 --> 00:11:16,260
Everyone else,

255
00:11:16,600 --> 00:11:18,480
take the positions I just assigned.

256
00:11:18,480 --> 00:11:19,600
If there are any issues,

257
00:11:19,600 --> 00:11:21,360
report to Captain Jiang immediately.

258
00:11:21,360 --> 00:11:22,080
Understood?

259
00:11:22,080 --> 00:11:22,810
Understood.

260
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,490
Move out.

261
00:11:28,440 --> 00:11:29,500
Hello, Godfather.

262
00:11:30,000 --> 00:11:31,240
Chen Hao has been arrested.

263
00:11:31,240 --> 00:11:31,760
Useless.

264
00:11:31,760 --> 00:11:32,690
Go hide quickly.

265
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:35,000
Chen Hao can't be trusted to keep his mouth shut.

266
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,200
Okay, got it.

267
00:11:46,640 --> 00:11:47,170
How is it?

268
00:12:08,320 --> 00:12:09,250
Why are you here?

269
00:12:11,120 --> 00:12:12,520
Why didn't you go abroad?

270
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:14,460
Do you think I can get away?

271
00:12:14,480 --> 00:12:15,400
Walking around openly like this

272
00:12:15,400 --> 00:12:16,330
is a dead end too.

273
00:12:16,800 --> 00:12:17,860
Leave me alone. Go!

274
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,200
Stop talking nonsense and come with me.

275
00:12:22,160 --> 00:12:22,620
Xiao Li.

276
00:12:23,760 --> 00:12:24,800
Brother Zhao, how is it?

277
00:12:24,800 --> 00:12:26,280
Captain Shen, nobody downstairs.

278
00:12:26,280 --> 00:12:27,210
Not here either.

279
00:12:27,960 --> 00:12:28,960
We're a step late.

280
00:12:29,520 --> 00:12:30,120
It's okay.

281
00:12:30,680 --> 00:12:31,360
Step up the surveillance.

282
00:12:31,360 --> 00:12:32,440
Issue a wanted poster.

283
00:12:32,440 --> 00:12:33,500
She won't get away.

284
00:12:34,040 --> 00:12:34,520
Let's go.

285
00:12:34,520 --> 00:12:34,840
Okay.

286
00:12:34,840 --> 00:12:35,370
Let's go.

287
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:41,480
Come in.

288
00:12:41,840 --> 00:12:42,700
It's safe here.

289
00:12:53,400 --> 00:12:54,860
Let me get some food first.

290
00:14:24,360 --> 00:14:25,960
Your hand hasn't healed yet?

291
00:14:27,600 --> 00:14:28,400
It won't heal.

292
00:14:31,760 --> 00:14:32,160
Here.

293
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:45,680
There's nothing else. Just make do.

294
